ractice \u003cem\u003eyoga\u003c/em\u003e where the sacred rivers like the Yamunā and the Ganges flow. But often this is not possible, especially for Westerners. The so-called \u003cem\u003eyoga\u003c/em\u003e societies in big cities may be successful in earning material benefit, but they are not at all suitable for the actual practice of \u003cem\u003eyoga.\u003c/em\u003e One who is not self-controlled and whose mind is not undisturbed cannot practice meditation. Therefore, in the \u003cem\u003eBṛhan-nāradīya Purāṇa\u003c/em\u003e it is said that in Kali-yuga (the present \u003cem\u003eyuga,\u003c/em\u003e or age), when people in general are short-lived, slow in spiritual realization and always disturbed by various anxieties, the best means of spiritual realization is chanting the holy name of the Lord.\"},{\"type\":\"content.Record\",\"title\":\"verse_text\",\"id\":1835,\"bb\":1623,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/6/11-12/b1623/\",\"body_value\":\"\u003cem\u003eharer nāma harer nāma\u003cbr /\u003eharer nāmaiva kevalam\u003cbr /\u003ekalau nāsty eva nāsty eva\u003cbr /\u003enāsty eva gatir anyathā\u003c/em\u003e\"},{\"type\":\"content.Record\",\"title\":\"paragraph\",\"id\":1836,\"bb\":1624,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/6/11-12/b1624/\",\"body_value\":\"“In this age of quarrel and hypocrisy the only means of deliverance is chanting the holy name of the Lord. There is no other way. There is no other way. There is no other way.”\"}]}],\"short_title\":\"Bg. 6.11-12\",\"medium_title\":\"Bhagavad-gītā As It Is 6.11-12\"},{\"id\":1837,\"meta\":{\"type\":\"books.Verse\",\"slug\":\"13-14\",\"show_in_menus\":false,\"seo_title\":\"\",\"search_description\":\"\",\"first_published_at\":null,\"alias_of\":null,\"locale\":\"en\"},\"title\":\"TEXTS 13-14\",\"advanced_view_url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/6/advanced-view/#bb1625\",\"language_menu\":[{\"display_name\":\"አማርኛ (Ethiopian)\",\"language_code\":\"am\",\"enabled\":false,\"url_path\":\"/am/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Български (Bulga