aya-vibhraṣṭaś\u003cbr /\u003echinnābhram iva naśyati\u003cbr /\u003eapratiṣṭho mahā-bāho\u003cbr /\u003evimūḍho brahmaṇaḥ pathi\u003c/em\u003e\"}]},{\"section\":\"synonyms\",\"section_title\":\"Books.Verse.synonyms\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"books.Synonyms\",\"title\":\"synonyms\",\"id\":2004,\"bb\":1773,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/6/38/b1773/\",\"shadow_value\":\"\u003cem\u003ekaccit\u003c/em\u003e – whether; \u003cem\u003ena\u003c/em\u003e – not; \u003cem\u003eubhaya\u003c/em\u003e – both; \u003cem\u003evibhraṣṭaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – deviated from; \u003cem\u003echinna\u003c/em\u003e – torn; \u003cem\u003eabhram\u003c/em\u003e – cloud; \u003cem\u003eiva\u003c/em\u003e – like; \u003cem\u003enaśyati\u003c/em\u003e – perishes; \u003cem\u003eapratiṣṭhaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – without any position; \u003cem\u003emahā-bāho\u003c/em\u003e – O mighty-armed Kṛṣṇa; \u003cem\u003evimūḍhaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – bewildered; \u003cem\u003ebrahmaṇaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – of transcendence; \u003cem\u003epathi\u003c/em\u003e – on the path.\",\"word_for_word_value\":[{\"word\":\"kaccit\",\"translation\":\"whether\"},{\"word\":\"na\",\"translation\":\"not\"},{\"word\":\"ubhaya\",\"translation\":\"both\"},{\"word\":\"vibhraṣṭaḥ\",\"translation\":\"deviated from\"},{\"word\":\"chinna\",\"translation\":\"torn\"},{\"word\":\"abhram\",\"translation\":\"cloud\"},{\"word\":\"iva\",\"translation\":\"like\"},{\"word\":\"naśyati\",\"translation\":\"perishes\"},{\"word\":\"apratiṣṭhaḥ\",\"translation\":\"without any position\"},{\"word\":\"mahā-bāho\",\"translation\":\"O mighty-armed Kṛṣṇa\"},{\"word\":\"vimūḍhaḥ\",\"translation\":\"bewildered\"},{\"word\":\"brahmaṇaḥ\",\"translation\":\"of transcendence\"},{\"word\":\"pathi\",\"translation\":\"on the path\"}]}]},{\"section\":\"translation\",\"section_title\":\"Books.Verse.translation\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"content.Record\",\"title\":\"translation\",\"id\":2005,\"bb\":1774,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/6/38/b1774/\",\"body_value\":\"O mighty-armed Kṛṣṇa