r one may fail, for many reasons. First of all, one may not be sufficiently serious about following the process. To pursue the transcendental path is more or less to declare war on the illusory energy. Consequently, whenever a person tries to escape the clutches of the illusory energy, she tries to defeat the practitioner by various allurements. A conditioned soul is already allured by the modes of material energy, and there is every chance of being allured again, even while performing transcendental disciplines. This is called \u003cem\u003eyogāc calita-mānasaḥ:\u003c/em\u003e deviation from the transcendental path. Arjuna is inquisitive to know the results of deviation from the path of self-realization."])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"e9:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1995-purport,1995-purport\",{\"className\":\"av-purport\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4\",\"children\":\"Purport\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L4a\",\"child-2000\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:31:child_items:4:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-base s-justify\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$12e\"}}]}]]]}]\nea:[\"$\",\"div\",\"2001-devanagari,2001-devanagari\",{\"className\":\"av-devanagari\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Devanagari\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L4a\",\"child-2002\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:32:child_items:0:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-lg text-center\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"कच्च‍िन्नोभयविभ्रष्टश्छिन्नाभ्रमिव नश्यति ।\u003cbr/\u003eअप्रतिष्ठो महाबाहो विमूढो ब्रह्मण: पथि ॥ ३८ ॥\"}}]}]]]}]\neb:[\"$\",\"div\",\"2001-verse_text,2001-verse_text\",{\"className\":\"av